			<p>We also have a stream, a hot climate (which will evaporate my lakes most of the year), lots of trees, thick vegetation, and the <a href="http://dwarffortresswiki.org/index.php/Surroundings" target="_blank">surroundings</a> are classified as Wilderness, which is middle ground for hostile wild life… not good, not evil.  Your surroundings will greatly effect your game, so check out the wiki for a brief guide.</p>
			<p>Time to <strong>"e"</strong>mbark!</p>
			<p>The next screen allows you to prepare your party before venturing forth.  You only have so many points to spend, so choose wisely!  The LNP has a few default templates which are very serviceable.  I’ll build my preferred party here for you by <strong>"preparing for the journey carefully"</strong>.</p>
